// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ct3cWs random domino pair tiling, 2023 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DlcyWs alternating domino tiling

// Tiling of randomly (horizontally/vertically) aligned pairs of domino tiles.
// Click to display domino outlines.

// tags: random, tiling, tesselation, domino, pair

